"\n"
"\n"
"I'd like to find some reeeally hot water to\n"
"relax in...<2.pa>but those fallin' rocks make it\n"
"way too dangerous."
msgstr ""

#. 1: sound
#. 2: pause (short)
#. 3: set_colour (blue)
