msgctxt "talk11"
msgid ""
"<1.so>It's rare to see a tourist like you<2.pa>\n"
"equipped to stand up to this heat.\n"
"\n"
"By the way, <3.se_co>Rudania <4.re_co>has settled down,<5.pa>\n"
"so feel free to take your time soakin'\n"
"in the hot springs."
msgstr ""

